Orange Bowl BoysChapter #11: PortalingShow NotesWe were down a man, but Toast and Scoop showed up well without Roman. Welcomed our newest sponsor and the Official Venue/Bar of the OBB…The Tank Brewing! We also welcomed Josh Pate from 247 and CBS Sports HQ for a pow-wow about his thoughts on the sudden transformation of the program. He was also cool enough to hang for 5 Questions! You’ll never guess which food he has eaten the most in his lfe…Lastly: SportsPodcastAwards.com has us as finalists in 2 categories: College Sports Podcast of the Year (Orange Bowl Boys) and Comedy Sports Podcast of the Year (Benched). We’d appreciate your votes! Just go to the website www.sportspodcastawards.com and click on us! ThanksSponsors: Ed Morse Automotive Group, LifeWallet, BeatinTheBookie.com, DraftKings, Caneswear & The Tank BrewingOrange Bowl Boys are owned and produced by OBB Media Inc.
